      <pubDate>Fri, 28 Mar 2025 05:10:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国的主要住房目标是受到警惕的房屋建筑商的摆布</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-28/the-uk-s-key-housing-target-is-at-the-mercy-of-wary-homebuilders</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国政府已将目标促进其增长计划中心的目标。实际上将交付这些房屋的公司已经告诉股东，他们将无法实现这一目标。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-28/the-uk-s-key-housing-target-is-at-the-mercy-of-wary-homebuilders</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 28 Mar 2025 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
